FBIS3-31716 "dreeu036_k_94007" FBIS-EEU-94-036 Document Type:Daily Report 23 Feb 1994 CROATIA Markac Appointed Deputy Interior Minister LD2202212794 Zagreb HTV Television in Serbo-Croatian 1830 GMT 22 Feb 94 LD2202212794 Zagreb HTV Television Language: Serbo-Croatian Article Type:BFN [Text] Republic of Croatia President Franjo Tudjman has decided to appoint Mladen Markac as deputy minister for internal affairs. The decision takes effect today.
